g a `TypeAttributeImpl`.\n- Verifies fallback delegation when the configured implementation does not implement the requested attribute.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per your instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0599039c72060ae80169f432e0a05881969edf4d75375daba7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 322, "output": 818, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23156, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777611477790, "responseId": "resp_0599039c72060ae80169f432d647fc8196b46f3ae62c4ab2f4"}, "toolResults": []}
